article.headline: Chris Mubiru leads Northwestern State over North Alabama 71-58
article.description: — Chris Mubiru had 13 points to lead Northwestern State to a 71-58 victory over North Alabama on Sunday.
article.linkText: Chris Mubiru leads Northwestern State over North Alabama 71-58
article.story: NATCHITOCHES, La. -- — Chris Mubiru had 13 points to lead Northwestern State to a 71-58 victory over North Alabama on Sunday. Mubiru finished 5 of 6 from the field for the Demons (3-4). Jerald Colonel scored 12 points and added six rebounds. Landyn Jumawan had 12 points with two 3-pointers. Jacari Lane finished with 14 points to lead the Lions (4-3). Will Soucie added 13 points and Canin Jefferson scored nine. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
